==Living former governors==

[[As of August 2007]], five former governors were alive, the oldest being [[Dale Bumpers]] (1971&ndash;1975, born 1925). The most recent governor to die was [[Sid McMath]] (1949&ndash;1953), on [[October 4]] [[2003]]. The most recently-serving governor to die was [[Frank D. White]] (1981&ndash;1983), on [[May 21]] [[2003]].

